sec.p:
For preoperative chemotherapy following SCRT, mFOLFOX6 regimen is to be given as follows:
oxaliplatin: 85 mg/m2 intravenously for 2 hours on day 1;
leucovorin calcium: 400 mg/m2 intravenously 2 hours before fluorouracil on day 1;
fluorouracil: 400 mg/m2 intravenously on day 1 and 2400 mg/m2 for 44–48 hours as continuous infusion. Cycles were repeated every 2 weeks for four cycles.
